window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A knife-wielding criminal threatens a rural Scottish idyll in the latest mystery from a well-loved author.... </p> <p>Life is good for Jane Highsmith and Roland Fox - Jane is planning on taking over the local veterinary practice, Rolandâ€™s second novel has been accepted for publication, and they are soon to be married. </p> <p>However, their wedding day is interrupted by a knife-wielding intruder. After confronting Jane in her surgery, she manages to inject the culprit with a microchip used for identifying pets. When a nearby petrol station is robbed by the same perpetrator, DI Fellowes and DS Bright hope that the microchip will lead them to the suspect....</p>"; 
